# This folder IS the live HERMES_HOME (bind-mounted). Allowlist: ignore everything,
# then re-include the curated files + the cs2 skills (ours and the ones Hermes
# writes). Runtime state (memory, sessions, node/, caches, .env) and the bundled
# skills stay ignored.
*
!.gitignore
!SOUL.md
!USER.md
!AGENTS.md
!config.yaml
!skills/
skills/*
!skills/cs2/

